BARNARD, Appellant, v. BROWN et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by Persons S. Barnard against Mary A Brown and another.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment appealed from affirmed, with costs.
